==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Goggler
<hw>Gog"gler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
carangoid oceanic fish (<spn>Trachurops crumenophthalmus</spn>), having
very large and prominent eyes; -- called also
<altname>goggle-eye</altname>, <altname>big-eyed scad</altname>, and
<altname>cicharra</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Goglet</ent>⟦br⟧
